review_text:
Convenient and clean metro station, near the Marc-Favreau library and bike paths.
There are still some construction going on but the elevators are in operation.
Not too crowded these days, hand sanitizer available and always full.

I was living there for over 5 years and I can say this station is safe,sooo windy during the winter and always under construction. the elevator was fine to be added, but last year one side was closed for I don't know what.
Great hub station and yuzu sushi is straight in front of the metro station!!! A must
How many stations have the elevators from the platforms to the ground level? This station does have the elevators (recently completed) and has been renovated.
The exterior is very nice since the renovations they added an elevator that come handy the only bad think is that there’s not soo many benches but other than that very good metro
Single exit. Simple layout

(Translated by Google) Ordinary station, not much to say.

(Original)
Station ordinaire,pas grand chose a dire.

(Translated by Google) Metro station that deserves some maintenance. It is dirty and rarely plows. I also question the relevance of allowing employees to park outside.

(Original)
Station de métro qui mériterais un peu d'entretien. C'est sale et rarement déneiger. Je m'interroge également sur la pertinence de permettre le stationnement des employés à l'extérieur.

(Translated by Google) The station is quite dirty. Very little maintained.

(Original)
La station est assez sale. Très peu entretenu.

(Translated by Google) Belle Station
Industrial district which is in full revival!
Housing complexes and condos and new green spaces

(Original)
Belle Station
Quartier industriel qui est en plein renouveau!
Complexes d’habitation et condos et nouveaux espaces verts

(Translated by Google) The exterior of the metro station is never maintained. It is very dirty.

(Original)
L'extérieur de la station de métro n'est jamais entretenu.  C'est très sale.

(Translated by Google) Station that is not well maintained.

(Original)
Station qui n'est pas bien entretenu.

(Translated by Google) The resort itself is not bad but the shops and nearby shops are not at the rendezvous. Because of this, you have to have a real reason to stop there. The Marc Favreau Library or the youth court are nearby. Otherwise, very few restaurants in the area.

(Original)
La station en soit n'est pas si mal mais les boutiques et magasins avoisinants ne sont pas au rendez-vous. De ce fait, il faut avoir une réelle raison de vous y arrêter. La bibliothèque Marc Favreau ou la cour de la jeunesse sont à proximité. Sinon, bien peu de restaurants dans les parages.

(Translated by Google) As the work has recently been completed, it is now possible to take the elevator from the metro exit to the top completely, where a shop allows you to make quick quick trips. Two exits, one leading to rue Saint-Vallier and the other, directly to boulevard Rosemont. A well maintained station, despite the rather large traffic at times.

(Original)
Les travaux ayant récemment été achevés, il est maintenant possible d'emprunter l’ascenseur à partir de la sortie du métro jusqu'au haut complètement, où un commerce permet de faire de petites courses rapides. Deux sorties, une menant à la rue Saint-Vallier et l'autre, directement au boulevard Rosemont. Une station bien entretenue, malgré l'achalandage plutôt important par moment.

(Translated by Google) Very good

(Original)
Très bien

(Translated by Google) Currently under construction, this station will receive elevators by the end of the year. This station will be more spacious and illuminated. Otherwise, it is very ordinary.

(Original)
Actuellement en travaux, cette station recevra des ascenseurs d'ici la fin de l'année. Cette station sera plus spacieuse et éclairée. Sinon, elle est bien ordinaire.

(Translated by Google) The elevators are functional now. Otherwise the station is very ordinary. Advantage near the library and the cycle path

(Original)
Les ascenseurs sont fonctionnels maintenant. Sinon la station est bien ordinaire. Avantage près de la bibliothèque et de la piste cyclable

(Translated by Google) Additional point for the elevator available and easily accessible.

(Original)
Point supplémentaire pour l'ascenseur disponible et facilement accessible.

(Translated by Google) The new design makes waiting for the bus a little shorter; if only there was something to cut off the freezing drafts !!!

(Original)
Le nouveau design rend un peu moins longue l'attente du bus ; si seulement il y avait quelque chose pour couper les courants d'air glaciaux !!!

(Translated by Google) The subway station is dirty ...

(Original)
La station de métro est sale...

(Original)
Pourquoi les escaliers roulants sont toujours hors fonction...
